  </indexterm>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to PCI Utils</title>

    <para>
      The <application>PCI Utils</application> package contains
      a set of programs for listing PCI devices, inspecting
      their status and setting their configuration registers.
    </para>

    &lfs121_checked;

